pink
Homonym Number:
Word Class:verb
Sense Number:
Definition:usu. pink 'em, to make a very good job of shearing a sheep (shearers sometimes call this a `special cut'), by shearing sheep close to the skin (sc ?make the pink skin show through (contrast rough'em)
